snippet.title: Wipe Out Arcade Ramtek 1974 - DICE 0.9 HD 1080p Gameplay
snippet.description:
Wipe Out is a competitive ball and paddle game where players try to keep the ball from getting into their goal while keeping their score from dropping down to zero.

It was produced by Ramtek in 1974 and released 15 different machines under this trade name, starting in 1973.

Other machines made by Ramtek during the time period Wipe Out was produced include Clean Sweep, Barricade, Hit Me, Sea Battle, Trivia, Hockey, Soccer, and Volly.

Source: https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=10453

Gameplay: DICE 0.9 1080p
